                  <summary><p>An incomplete <title xml:lang="ta">Tiruvātavūrārpurāṇam</title>, a poem on the life of <persName>Māṇikkavācakar</persName>, by <persName role="author">Kaṭavuṇmāmuṉivar</persName> (15th century?). See Sweetman &amp; Ilakkuvan (2012, p. 66), Zvelebil (1995, p. 334, 405).</p>
